  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba3\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb1\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "It is a mistake for Prime Minister Ranil to agree to work with a corrupt government - Sumanthiran",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "President's Counsel MA Sumanthiran, a TNA spokesman and parliamentarian who has insisted that the Sri Lankan People's Alliance should not be involved in any interim measures as the country faces a major economic crisis, and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe have erred in agreeing to work with a corrupt government.",
        "Mark Meloch-Brown, a prominent British diplomat, stressed in a post on his official Twitter page that International Monetary Fund (IMF) officials need to find out why Sri Lanka is facing a major economic crisis.",
        "MP MA Sumanthiran said this in a post on his official Twitter page quoting his post.",
        "'This is why I urge all members of the Sri Lanka People's Alliance, including President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, to resign.",
        "It is only right that the United People's Power and the People's Liberation Front should make this a condition.",
        "Similarly, it is wrong for Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe to agree to work with a government that is rife with corruption, \u201dhe said in the post."
      ],
